{"name":"Gauntlet","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/fist/fist-rondel-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A reinforced gauntlet designed for combat, capable of delivering powerful blows while keeping the hand protected.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Finesse</td><td>Melee d4 (B/P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Deflect, Disarm, Nimble, Riposte</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":3,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When hit with a melee attack, as a reaction before damage is dealt, attempt a Disarm. If you successfully disarm the attacker, you take no damage and possess the weapon."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Cane Sword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-straight-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A gentleman's walking cane that conceals a slender blade, equally useful as a social accessory and a deadly weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse</td><td>Melee d6 (B/P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Entangle, Puncture, Riposte, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":35,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"While dual wielding the cane and sword together, the cane gains Deflect d8. Hitting with the cane deals your DEX modifier in damage (minimum 1), and you gain advantage on your next attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Compass Blade","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-curved-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A precision-engineered clockwork throwing blade that unfolds in flight, making it deadly at range as well as in melee.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse</td><td>Melee 2d4 (P/S), Thrown 2d4 (40/60)</td><td>Clockwork, Keen, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":100,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When deployed as a Double Ended attack, the attack gains advantage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hidden Blade","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-straight-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A clockwork wrist-mounted blade that deploys on demand, ideal for assassination and ambush.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Finesse</td><td>Melee d4 (P)</td><td>Clockwork, Conceal, Nimble, Slip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":75,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Surprised creatures take maximum damage from this weapon and any attachments."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Knuckle Axe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-broad-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact axe blade mounted on a knuckle guard, combining the striking power of an axe with the mobility of a fist weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (P/S)</td><td>Deflect, Conceal, Keen</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you reduce a creature to 0 HP, make one additional attack. When wielding two knuckle axes, extra attacks also trigger on a critical hit. Once per attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Interceptor","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/fist/fist-knuckles-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A hardened parrying device worn on the forearm or hand, designed primarily to intercept attacks and deflect incoming blows.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Finesse</td><td>Melee (B)</td><td>Conceal, Deflect (d6)</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":3,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Deflect can be used against ranged weapon attacks. When you can see a target within 5 feet, use your reaction to impose disadvantage on their attack roll."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Katar","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-curved-white.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A push dagger with a horizontal hand grip, allowing the wielder to punch with lethal force and cut with exceptional control.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Keen, Nimble</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you score a powerful blow (critical hit), make one additional attack as part of the same action. If dual wielding katars, this extra attack also activates for the off-hand katar."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Punch Dagger","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-short-green.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A tiny blade mounted horizontally across the knuckles, making it nearly invisible in the hand and ideal for close-quarters ambushes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P)</td><td>Conceal, Nimble, Punch</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":0.5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You have advantage on attacks made outside of your turn. If wielding this weapon in your off-hand, you may make an opportunity attack with both weapons."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Side Baton","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/fist/fist-knuckles-red.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A short baton with a perpendicular side handle, granting exceptional leverage for blocking and striking.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (B)</td><td>Deflect, Riposte</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"+1 to weapon AC. Deflect increases to d10, and you may add your proficiency bonus to Deflect rolls."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Fan","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/daggers/dagger-serrated-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>An ornate war fan with razor-edged metal tines, capable of being used folded as a bludgeon or unfolded as a slashing and piercing weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (B/P/S)</td><td>Conceal, Keen, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>While unfolded:</em> Deflect 2d6 vs ranged attacks. <em>While folded:</em> Gains Stagger and Melee d6.</p>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Ambush Weapons","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"While unfolded, Deflect increases to 2d6 against ranged attacks. While folded, the fan gains Stagger and its melee damage becomes d6."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Battle Axe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-battle-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A reliable single-bladed axe sized for one-handed use, capable of devastating sweeping blows and powerful two-handed grip.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Versatile</td><td>Melee d8 (S), Versatile d10</td><td>Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":"battleaxe"},"properties":["ver"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Reroll 1s and 2s on damage dice. When wielded two-handed, the axe also gains Thrown with a damage die of d12 (20/60 ft range)."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Broadaxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-broad-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A wide-headed two-handed axe designed for maximum cutting surface, ideal for cleaving through armor and shield alike.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy</td><td>Melee 2d6 (S)</td><td>Punch, Sunder</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On a mighty blow (critical hit), the target is Staggered and cannot make a saving throw to resist the condition."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Greataxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-great-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A massive two-handed axe that trades subtlety for raw destructive power, capable of felling enemies and disarming them in one sweep.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy</td><td>Melee d12 (S)</td><td>Disarm, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":20,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":"greataxe"},"properties":["hvy","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On a mighty blow (critical hit), add one additional damage die to the total damage dealt."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Halberd","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-halberd-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A pole weapon combining an axe blade with a spear tip and hook, offering versatile attack options at extended reach.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach</td><td>Melee 2d6 (P/S)</td><td>Brace, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":35,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":7,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":"halberd"},"properties":["hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Trip attacks made with this weapon impose disadvantage on the target's saving throw to resist being knocked prone."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Handaxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-hand-black.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A small, single-headed axe light enough to be thrown or used as an off-hand weapon, reliable and easy to carry in multiples.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (S), Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":"handaxe"},"properties":["lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you miss a Disarm attack, you may reroll the attack and take the new result."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hook Sword","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-broad-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A crescent-bladed sword with a hooked tip, excellent for catching enemy weapons and creating openings in combat.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d6 (S)</td><td>Disarm, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Two hook swords can be hooked together to gain Reach and Versatile d8.</p>"},"price":{"value":30,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On a melee hit, use your reaction to attempt a Disarm or Entangle as a bonus. When two hook swords are linked together, they gain Reach and deal Versatile d8 damage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Kama","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-hand-worn.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A small sickle-like weapon derived from a farming tool, fast and precise enough to be thrown or used in pairs.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P/S), Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Keen, Nimble</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Keen adds 2 extra damage dice instead of 1. An off-hand kama adds its Keen bonus to the main-hand attack as well."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Palm Axe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-great-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A massive two-handed reaching axe with a broad curved blade, designed to sweep multiple targets in a single action.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach</td><td>Melee 2d6 (P/S)</td><td>Brace, Keen, Puncture, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":45,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","rch","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As an action, attack each creature within your reach. Until the start of your next turn, ranged attackers suffer disadvantage against you."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Poleaxe","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-halberd-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A versatile pole weapon bearing axe, hammer, and spike heads, capable of bludgeoning, piercing, slashing, and blocking in a single weapon.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy</td><td>Melee d10 (B/P/S)</td><td>Brace, Deflect, Punch, Puncture, Stagger, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":40,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":7,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","two"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"+1 to weapon AC. You may add your proficiency bonus to Deflect rolls made with this weapon."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Tomahawk","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/axes/axe-throwing.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A light, balanced throwing axe with a broad curved blade, designed for hurling at range as much as fighting in melee.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Damage</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Basic</strong></td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light</td><td>Melee d4 (P/S), Thrown (40/120)</td><td>Slip, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Axes","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On a mighty blow (critical hit), the target has disadvantage on their next attack roll."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
